  "detailed_description": "Virage Rally is a rally racing game with procedurally generated stages.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Never race the same stage twice</h2>All stages are procedurally generated: each of the turn, bump, ditch and crest of the stage are unique. Each stage has its own parameters that defines the shape of the road: straight/curve, smooth/bumpy, wide/narrow and flatland/hill.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245630/extras/6c6ddb190518e17fc4e8a6c9fec427a0.poster.avif?t=1582737407\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245630/extras/6c6ddb190518e17fc4e8a6c9fec427a0.webm?t=1582737407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245630/extras/6c6ddb190518e17fc4e8a6c9fec427a0.mp4?t=1582737407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Compete against AI drivers in championship or single rally mode</h2>Take part in the championship that will test your driving skills in 5 locations. Stages are up to 25km long and take place on dirt, asphalt, snow; at daytime, nighttime or in the fog.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245630/extras/51b22c7eb2cf3d176d5ec782255b97c1.poster.avif?t=1582737407\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245630/extras/51b22c7eb2cf3d176d5ec782255b97c1.webm?t=1582737407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245630/extras/51b22c7eb2cf3d176d5ec782255b97c1.mp4?t=1582737407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Fully moddable</h2>Create your own rally/championship or import your car model and physics.",
